			<p>grasping for straws! when you will stand before God, it wont be to chit chat about nonsense about thinking things over, it will be for judgment for all eternity and the consequences each of us brought on ourselves. trust me, there is a hell far beyond anything you can dream up or deny.</p>
			
			
