			<p>Approximately a single century later, Murray finally came up with an answer. He called out to The Voice, who appeared at once.<br />
The Voice said, &#8220;So you have finally come to a conclusion?&#8221;<br />
&#8220;I have,&#8221; Murray said.<br />
The Voice, ever so calm, paused &#8230;for a moment, as if considering its next words.<br />
&#8220;And what have you concluded?&#8221; asked The Voice.<br />
Murray paused, gathered his thoughts, and smiled inwardly with the greatest capacity.<br />
&#8220;Forty two.&#8221;</p>
			
			
