<p>&#8220;Mental masturbation&#8221; is as healthy and normal as regular masturbation, and everyone participates in it. It exercises the mind and is the foundation of all art &#8211; whether or not the creation is any good, is based solely upon the complexity of the exercise and therefore the participants&#8217; immersion.</p>
