				</cite>
				<div style="clear:both"></div>
			</div>		

			
			</div>

			<p>It&#8217;s &#8220;The Egg&#8221;, by Andy Weir. Here&#8217;s a link: <a href="http://www.galactanet.com/oneoff/theegg_mod.html" rel="nofollow">http://www.galactanet.com/oneoff/theegg_mod.html</a></p>
			
			
